OL,7,FThe finance minister has paused rates
OL,8,Fbills for Belfast's Victoria Square
OL,9,Fapartment owners - five years after
OL,10,Fthey were forced to leave their homes.
OL,12,FCaoimhe Archibald said legal action
OL,13,Fhas also been paused on those facing
OL,14,Flegal action for not paying their bill.
OL,16,FShe said she was working with
OL,17,Fministerial colleagues and her focus
OL,18,Fwas on finding a solution.
