OL,7,FUlster Garden Villages welcomed the
OL,8,Fstatement from the finance minister.JA
OL,9,Fspokesperson said: "This is the first
OL,10,Fpiece of good news that Ulster Garden
OL,11,FVillages has received in relation to
OL,12,Fthe Victoria Square Apartments since
OL,13,F2019. We note that the Northern
OL,14,FIreland Executive is currently engaged
OL,15,Fand willing to take action around the
OL,16,Fplight of the owners; there is no
OL,17,Fdoubt that this is a very positive
OL,18,Ffirst step.J"Going forward it is the
OL,19,Flegislative change that will make a
OL,20,Flasting difference. With that in mind
OL,21,Fwe hope to engage with the political
OL,22,Fparties including the minister for
OL,23,Fcommunities to ascertain how these
OL,24,Fchanges can take place in a timely and
OL,25,Feffective manner.
